after Dinner to Some Pub on the way to Clevedon, then Got All Smoochy when She Got Back. By that time I Was Pretty Pissed off to Be Fair. Like I'd Been away for 48 Hours Pretty Much, and Said Some Pretty Big Stuff, so Talking about that Would've Been a Good Idea, Surely?","uuid":"A6D874E5AB6C4D68AF6AEBEBB8942E3D"}},
